text: Hello <!everyone>. My name is Charles-Eugene LOUBAO. I am an Android developer and International Student currently located in Dover Delaware. I am looking for a Job related to Android development. Since I am in Delaware I am looking for a position in Dover or a position where I can work remotely (If possible)

Hi All, I'm Paul - I'm from Odecee - <http://odecee.com.au/careers/> we are a small(ish) but rapid growing consultancy in Melbourne and Sydney (thats Australia) who are always hiring talented consulting engineers across the stack.  We partner with key enterprise clients and make internal and external applications (much more exciting than that sounds I promise) so check our the site for more details.  Oh and happy to offer sponsorship to get you here.  <mailto:pjenkins@odecee.com.au|pjenkins@odecee.com.au> is me.  Im looking to hire about 150 new team members, mostly Melbourne with some in Sydney.  So join, and bring friends (referral bonuses….) but main reason is you get to work with cool people, project work, CBD, focus on innovation and awesome culture with lots of variety.  <http://odecee.com.au/careers/> for more details or me at <mailto:pjenkins@odecee.com.au|pjenkins@odecee.com.au> - We do a lot but Android is there - also Responsive Web (Front End), API/Server (Back-End), Full Stack, Test Automation, iOS, Agile BA, UX Designers and Visual Designers, might be more
